## Development

### Running Tests

```bash
# Install dev dependencies
pip install -e ".[all,dev]"

# Run tests
pytest tests/ -v

# Run with coverage
pytest tests/ --cov=caema_utils --cov-report=term-missing
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Format code
black src/ tests/

# Lint
ruff src/ tests/

# Type check
mypy src/
```

